<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Book Notes</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
    
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>BOOKS I'VE READ üìö</h1>
        <a id="newPostBtn" href="/new">New Post</a>
        <p>Welcome! ü§ù Here you can create detailed notes ‚úç for each of the books you have ever read. Please note that when creating a new post we use the <strong>ISBN</strong> number to collect the cover for your book using an API. So be careful and make sure you are inserting the correct number.</p>
        <p>Sorted with <strong>my top recommendations</strong> up top. Sort by:  <a href="/title">title</a>,  <a href="/newest">newest</a>,  or  <a href="/best">best</a></p>
        <hr>
        <ul id="postsList">
          <% notes.forEach(note => { %>
            <li class="book-item">
              <% if (note.image) { %>
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,<%= note.image %>" alt="Book Cover">
              <% } %>
              <div class="content">
                <h2>
                  <%=note.title.toUpperCase()%> - BY <%=note.authors.toUpperCase()%>
                </h2>
                <small>
                  DATE READ:üìñ <%=new Date(note.date_read).toLocaleDateString()%>
                </small>
                <small>
                  HOW STRONGLY I RECOMMEND IT:üëç <%=note.rating %>/10 
                </small>
                <p>
                  <%=note.notes%>
                </p>              
                <a class="edit" href="/edit/<%= note.id %>">Edit</a>
                <a class="delete" href="/delete/<%= note.id %>">Delete</a>
              </div>
            </li>
          <% }); %>
        </ul>
    </div>     
</body>
</html>